    Package Description
    com.st.st25sdk.type4a.st25ta
    Defines all Tags classes to handle ST25TA series The ST25TA series are an NFC Forum Type 4 Tags; Tags communicate using the ISO/IEC 14443 Type A protocol.
    com.st.st25sdk.type5.st25dvpwm  
    com.st.st25sdk.type5.st25tv
    Provides classes to handle ST25TV Tags (NFC Forum Type5) from STMicroelectronics.
